  "description": {
   "en": "The story of Ryo Kitakami, a 14-year-old boy who killed a man and was released from a juvenile training school. After being released from prison, Ryo wanders the town, swearing revenge on his father, who drove his mother and sister to their deaths, and chasing a drug organization. Chasing the tragedy, tough and hard car action and gunfight. A serious action story that gives off a strong mood like a black-and-white chivalrous movie. ──It's not a gag. Not hot-blooded. Here is Makoto Kobayashi's unfinished and unique work released during the \"big newcomer\" era of the masterpiece \"1.2 Sanshiro\"!"
